  "texts": [
    "Here, the robot-active mechanism was developed by the Magneto-Rheological (MR) actuators which have advancements in terms of superior torque, flexibility control, and minimal power.",
    "In this model, the MR actuator works as a clutch and transferred the torque in the robotic joint safely.",
    "The MR actuator acts as a brake to offer higher resistance for helping the strengthen muscles.",
    "Further, the human intention levels were computed by placing the EMG on the skin surface.",
    "The efficiency of the implemented model was weighted with impedancebased techniques and achieved higher effectualness than the traditional mechanism.Psychoula et al."
